        <body>
            <pb n="1R"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Barbados</placeName>. <date>31 Jan 1844</date>—</p>
            <p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir.</p>
            <p rend="indent(3)">I have had this pleasure<lb/> at <placeName>Grenada</placeName>
                since which my Father &amp; self have<lb/> arrived here were we found all the
                family<lb/> well. I was put in possession of your esteemed favor<lb/> to Da Mother
                and the nos 10 of the Occident. I<lb/> believe I informed you before that
                    <persName>Mr. I Lindo</persName> had<lb/> not taken his Numbers. I also inform
                you that my<lb/> Father is a subscriber and he forwarded the amt of
                subscription<lb/> please forward the future nos. address to him instead of<lb/>
                myself. I take great pleasure in transmitting<lb/> on the organ of the society. The
                minutes of a meeting<lb/> called at the request of the Ladies of the
                Congregation<lb/> for the purpose of forming a Jewish Sunday school.<lb/> I know you
                will feel pleased to <del>know</del> find that my<lb/> sister
                    <persName>Julia</persName> was the promoter of the institution. I also<lb/>
                forward the address of <persName>E A Moses Esq.</persName> which I can hope<lb/>
                will find a suitable place in your “Occident.” Enclosed<lb/> is also a letter from
                    <persName>A Finzi Esq.</persName> which you will also<lb/> notice in<add>?</add>
                to the <placeName>Barbados</placeName> Congregation. I have no<lb/> time to enlarge
                as the <sic>vessell</sic> sails almost immediately<lb/> with best <add>?</add> I
                remain Dear Sir<lb/> Yours ever truly</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">
                <persName role="author">SevCarvalho</persName>
            </p>
            <pb n="1V"/>
            <p rend="indent(5)">
                <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
